#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kontact; is the integrated solution for personal information management. It "
"combines the well-known &kde; applications for email, scheduling and address "
"book (&kmail;, &korganizer;, &kaddressbook;) into a single interface. Being "
"based on a true component framework &kontact; provides exactly the same "
"functionality as the stand-alone applications, and adds more features, by "
"making use of the integrated way &kontact; runs the applications as "
"components. Users still retain the choice of which applications are run "
"within &kontact; and which are run stand-alone."
msgstr ""
"&kontact; je integrirana rešitev za upravljanje osebnih podatkov. Združuje "
"znane &kde; aplikacije za e-pošto, planiranje, adresar in beležke (&kmail;, "
"&korganizer;, &kaddressbook; in &knotes;) v en sam vmesnik. Ker temelji na "
"pravem ogrodju komponent &kontact; zagotavlja popolnoma enako funkcionalnost "
"kot samostojne aplikacije in dodaja več zmožnosti z uporabo integriranega "
"načina &kontact; izvaja aplikacije kot komponente. Uporabniki še vedno "
"obdržijo izbiro, katere aplikacije se izvajajo znotraj &kontact; in katere "
"se izvajajo samostojno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition to the functionality of the individual applications, &kontact; "
"provides a summary view and advanced drag &amp; drop features between "
"components."
msgstr ""
"Poleg funkcionalnosti posameznih aplikacij ponuja &kontact; pogled povzetka "
"in napredno zmožnost povleci &amp; spusti med komponentami."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kontact; Components"
msgstr "&kontact; Komponente"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kontact; integrates the following applications. See the individual "
"application manuals for details on how to use them. These apply to running "
"them as components inside &kontact; just as well as running them stand-alone."
msgstr ""
"&kontact; vključuje naslednje aplikacije. Za podrobnosti o njihovi uporabi "
"glejte priročnike za posamezne aplikacije. To velja za njihovo izvajanje kot "
"komponent znotraj &kontact; enako dobro, kot da jih izvajate samostojno."

