#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &kontact; Main Window"
msgstr "&kontact; Glavno okno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Main Window consists of a side pane on the left showing the icons of the "
"available components, a main view on the right which contains the main "
"window of the active component and the usual menu, tool and status bars."
msgstr ""
"Glavno okno je sestavljeno iz stranskega podokna na levi, ki prikazuje ikone "
"razpoložljivih komponent, glavnega pogleda na desni, ki vsebuje glavno okno "
"aktivne komponente ter običajne menijske, orodne in statusne vrstice."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "Side Pane"
msgstr "Stransko podokno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Side Pane serves multiple purposes. It allows for switching between "
"components, shows which component is active and serves as the target for "
"drag &amp; drop operations to the different applications."
msgstr ""
"Stransko podokno ima več namenov. Omogoča preklapljanje med komponentami, "
"prikazuje, katera komponenta je aktivna in služi kot cilj za vlečenje &amp; "
"spustite operacije v različne aplikacije."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kontact;'s Side Pane</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kontact; stransko podokno</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kontact;'s Side Pane</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Stransko podokno &kontact;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>&kontact;'s Side Pane</para>"
msgstr "<para>Stransko podokno &kontact;</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For switching between components simply click on the corresponding icon. The "
"main window of the component is shown and the menu, tool and status bars are "
"adapted to reflect the functionality of the active component. If you "
"activate a component for the first time there might be a small delay until "
"the main view is changed, because components are loaded on demand. This "
"means you don't waste memory for components not in use."
msgstr ""
"Za preklapljanje med komponentami preprosto kliknite na ustrezno ikono. "
"Prikaže se glavno okno komponente, meni, orodne in statusne vrstice pa so "
"prilagojene tako, da odražajo funkcionalnost aktivne komponente. Če "
"komponento aktivirate prvič, lahko pride do spremembe glavnega pogleda z "
"majhno zamudo, ker se komponente naložijo na zahtevo. To pomeni, da ne "
"zapravljate pomnilnika za komponente, ki niso v uporabi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The icons in the Side Pane can also be used as targets for drag &amp; drop "
"operations. For example, you can drag a mail message from the mail part and "
"drop it on the icon of the to-do list or the calendar to create a to-do or "
"event associated with this mail."
msgstr ""
"Ikone v stranskem podoknu lahko uporabite tudi kot cilje za vlečenje &amp; "
"padajoče operacije. Na primer, lahko povlečete e-poštno sporočilo iz "
"poštnega dela in ga spustite na ikono seznama opravil ali koledarja, da "
"ustvarite opravilo ali dogodek, povezan s to pošto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finally, you can change the size of the icons in the Side Pane. Right-"
"clicking on the Side Pane will give you the option to use Large, Normal, or "
"Small icons, as well as the option to use text only instead of icons."
msgstr ""
"Nazadnje lahko spremenite velikost ikon v stranskem podoknu. Z desnim klikom "
"na stransko podokno boste imeli možnost uporabe velikih, običajnih ali "
"majhnih ikon ter možnost uporabe samo besedila namesto ikon."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you dislike the Side Pane, you can simply hide it by dragging the "
"splitter. An alternative navigation between parts is provided by the "
"<guilabel>Navigator</guilabel> toolbar, which can be freely positioned. See "
"<xref linkend=\"bars\"/> for more on the <guilabel>Navigator</guilabel> "
"toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Če vam stransko podokno ni všeč, ga lahko preprosto skrijete tako, da "
"povlečete razdelilnik. Alternativno krmarjenje med deli omogoča orodna "
"vrstica <guilabel>Navigator</guilabel>, ki jo lahko poljubno postavite. "
"Glejte <xref linkend=\"bars\"/> za več o orodni vrstici <guilabel>Navigator</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main View"
msgstr "Glavni pogled"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The view on the right which takes up most of the area of the &kontact; main "
"window shows the active component. This exactly corresponds to the main "
"window the component uses when run as a stand-alone application. The "
"highlighted icon in the Side Pane indicates to which application the Main "
"View belongs. &kontact; remembers the active component when exiting, so the "
"next time &kontact; starts it initially displays that component in the Main "
"View."
msgstr ""
"Pogled na desni, ki zavzema večino območja &kontact; glavno okno prikazuje "
"aktivno komponento. To natančno ustreza glavnemu oknu, ki ga komponenta "
"uporablja, ko se izvaja kot samostojna aplikacija. Označena ikona v "
"stranskem podoknu označuje, kateri aplikaciji pripada glavni pogled. "
"&kontact; si zapomni aktivno komponento ob izhodu, tako da naslednjič, ko "
"&kontact; zažene, sprva prikaže to komponento v glavnem pogledu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kontact;'s Main View</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Glavni pogled &kontact;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kontact;'s Main View</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Glavni pogled &kontact;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>&kontact;'s Main View</para>"
msgstr "<para>Glavni pogled &kontact;</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition, there are two ways of overriding the component that &kontact; "
"starts with. The first is supplying an argument to the &kontact; program "
"call (see <xref linkend=\"command-line\"/>). The second is a setting in the "
"&kontact; Settings dialog that will allow you to always start &kontact; in a "
"certain mode."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega obstajata dva načina za preglasitev komponente, ki jo &kontact; "
"se začne z. Prvi je posredovanje argumenta &kontact;u klic programa (glejte "
"<xref linkend=\"command-line\"/>). Druga je nastavitev v &kontact; Pogovorno "
"okno z nastavitvami, ki vam bo omogočilo, da vedno zaženete &kontact; v "
"določenem načinu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To get to it, go to <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure &kontact;</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and click on "
"<guilabel>Kontact</guilabel> in the list."
msgstr ""
"Do njega pridete tako, da pojdite na <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kontact;</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in "
"na seznamu kliknite <guilabel>Kontact</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kontact; Starting Component Setting</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kontact; Začetek nastavitve komponent</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kontact; Starting Component Setting</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kontact; Začetek nastavitve komponent</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>&kontact; Starting Component Setting</para>"
msgstr "<para>&kontact; Začetek nastavitve komponent</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu, Tool and Status Bars"
msgstr "Meni, orodna in statusna vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The menu, tool and status bars are adapted to the active component. That "
"means that, in addition to some common functions like the help menu which "
"are shown for all components, there are actions which are switched when the "
"active component is switched. These actions available for each component are "
"the same as those available when running the application stand-alone."
msgstr ""
"Meni, orodna in statusna vrstica so prilagojene aktivni komponenti. To "
"pomeni, da poleg nekaterih običajnih funkcij, kot je meni za pomoč, ki so "
"prikazani za vse komponente, obstajajo dejanja, ki se preklopijo, ko "
"preklopite aktivno komponento. Ta dejanja, ki so na voljo za vsako "
"komponento, so enaka tistim, ki so na voljo, ko se aplikacija izvaja "
"samostojno."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:234 index.docbook:247 index.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>Views of &kontact;'s menubars in the Summary View, Mail View, "
"and Calendar View</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Pogledi menijskih vrstic &kontact; v pogledu povzetka, pogledu "
"pošte in pogledu koledarja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:240 index.docbook:253 index.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>Views of &kontact;'s menubars in the Summary View, Mail View, and "
"Calendar View</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Pogledi menijskih vrstic &kontact; v pogledu povzetka, pogledu pošte "
"in pogledu koledarja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Views of &kontact;'s menubars in the Summary View, Mail View, and Calendar "
"View."
msgstr ""
"Pogledi menijskih vrstic &kontact; v pogledu povzetka, pogledu pošte in "
"pogledu koledarja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition, &kontact; can show the <guilabel>Navigator</guilabel> toolbar, "
"which allows you access to the &kontact; components very much as the Side "
"Pane does. However, unlike the Side Pane, buttons in the "
"<guilabel>Navigator</guilabel> toolbar cannot be used for drag &amp; drop "
"operations to other components."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega &kontact; lahko prikaže orodno vrstico <guilabel>Navigator</"
"guilabel>, ki vam omogoča dostop do &kontact; komponente zelo podobno kot "
"stransko podokno. Za razliko od stranskega podokna pa gumbov v orodni "
"vrstici <guilabel>Navigator</guilabel> ni mogoče uporabiti za vlečenje &amp; "
"spustite operacije na druge komponente."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To activate the toolbar, select <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Toolbars Shown</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Navigator</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite aktivirati orodno vrstico, izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Prikazane orodne "
"vrstice</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Navigator</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>&kontact;'s <guimenuitem>Navigator</guimenuitem> toolbar.</"
"screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kontact; orodna vrstica <guimenuitem>Navigator</guimenuitem>.</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>&kontact;'s <guimenuitem>Navigator</guimenuitem> toolbar.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&kontact; orodna vrstica <guimenuitem>Navigator</guimenuitem>.</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>&kontact;'s <guimenuitem>Navigator</guimenuitem> toolbar.</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Orodna vrstica <guimenuitem>Navigator</guimenuitem> &kontact;.</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A special action common to all components is the <guimenuitem>New</"
"guimenuitem> action. It allows creation of new objects including emails, "
"contacts, appointments and to-dos independently of which component is "
"active. The component responsible for processing the selected object is "
"started, if required, and takes over the created object."
msgstr ""
"Posebno dejanje, skupno vsem komponentam, je dejanje <guimenuitem>Novo</"
"guimenuitem>. Omogoča ustvarjanje novih predmetov, vključno z e-pošto, "
"stiki, sestanki in opravili, ne glede na to, katera komponenta je aktivna. "
"Komponenta, odgovorna za obdelavo izbranega objekta, se po potrebi zažene in "
"prevzame izdelani objekt."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kontact;'s New Menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nov meni &kontact;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kontact;'s New Menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kontact; Novi meni</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>&kontact;'s New Menu</para>"
msgstr "<para>Nov meni &kontact;</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid "Drag and Drop Functionality"
msgstr "Funkcionalnost povleci in spusti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kontact; provides advanced drag and drop functionality between the programs "
"it contains. Following is a brief description of each of the specific drag "
"and drop operations that can be used and the result of each."
msgstr ""
"&kontact; zagotavlja napredno funkcijo povleci in spusti med programi, ki "
"jih vsebuje. Sledi kratek opis posameznih operacij povleci in spusti, ki jih "
"je mogoče uporabiti, ter rezultat vsake."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmail; -&gt; &korganizer; To-do List"
msgstr "&kmail; -&gt; &korganizer; Seznam opravil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Dragging a message from <ulink url=\"help:/kmail2/using-kmail.html#the-mail-"
"reader-window\">&kmail;'s Headers pane</ulink> to the icon for "
"&korganizer;'s To-do list (<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"todo-list-sidebar-icon.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon>) will create a new To-do with "
"<guilabel>Mail: <replaceable>Subject</replaceable></guilabel> as the title "
"and <guilabel>From: <replaceable>Sender</replaceable> To: "
"<replaceable>Receiver</replaceable> Subject: <replaceable>Subject</"
"replaceable></guilabel> as the contents (where text that looks "
"<guilabel><replaceable>like this</replaceable></guilabel> is information "
"from the message itself), as well as the email message itself as an "
"attachment."
msgstr ""
"Vlečenje sporočila iz <ulink url=\"help:/kmail2/using-kmail.html#the-mail-"
"reader-window\">podokna z glavami &kmail;</ulink> na ikono za opravila "
"&korganizer; seznam (<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"todo-list-sidebar-icon.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject></guiicon>) bo ustvaril nov Opravila z <guilabel>Pošta: "
"<replaceable>Zadeva</replaceable></guilabel> kot naslov in <guilabel>Od: "
"<replaceable>Pošiljatelj</replaceable> Za: <replaceable>Prejemnik</"
"replaceable> Zadeva: <replaceable>Zadeva</replaceable></guilabel> kot "
"vsebina (kjer je besedilo, ki je videti <guilabel><replaceable>tako</"
"replaceable></guilabel>, informacije iz samega sporočila), kot tudi e-poštno "
"sporočilo sama kot priloga."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmail; -&gt; &korganizer; Calendar"
msgstr "&kmail; -&gt; &korganizer; Koledar"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Dragging a message from <ulink url=\"help:/kmail2/using-kmail.html#the-mail-"
"reader-window\">&kmail;'s Headers pane</ulink> to the icon for "
"&korganizer;'s Calendar (<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"calendar-sidebar-icon.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon>) will create a new Event with "
"<guilabel>Mail: <replaceable>Subject</replaceable></guilabel> as the title "
"and <guilabel>From: <replaceable>Sender</replaceable> To: "
"<replaceable>Receiver</replaceable> Subject: <replaceable>Subject</"
"replaceable></guilabel> as the contents (where text that looks "
"<guilabel><replaceable>like this</replaceable></guilabel> is information "
"from the message itself), as well as the email message itself as an "
"attachment."
msgstr ""
"Vlečenje sporočila iz <ulink url=\"help:/kmail2/using-kmail.html#the-mail-"
"reader-window\">podokna z glavami &kmail;</ulink> na ikono za koledar "
"&korganizer; (<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"calendar-sidebar-icon.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject></guiicon>) bo ustvaril nov dogodek z <guilabel> Pošta: "
"<replaceable>Zadeva</replaceable></guilabel> kot naslov in <guilabel>Od: "
"<replaceable>Pošiljatelj</replaceable> Za: <replaceable>Prejemnik</"
"replaceable> Zadeva: <replaceable>Zadeva</replaceable ></guilabel> kot "
"vsebino (kjer je besedilo, ki je videti <guilabel><replaceable>tako</"
"replaceable></guilabel>, informacije iz samega sporočila), kot tudi samo e-"
"poštno sporočilo kot prilogo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:382 index.docbook:425 index.docbook:449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that dragging onto the To-do button creates a To-do, whereas dragging "
"onto the Calendar creates an Event. More on this distinction is available in "
"the <ulink url=\"help:/korganizer\">&korganizer; documentation</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da vlečenje na gumb Opravila ustvari opravilo, medtem ko "
"vlečenje na koledar ustvari dogodek. Več o tem razlikovanju je na voljo v "
"<ulink url=\"help:/korganizer\">&korganizer; dokumentacija</ulink>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmail; -&gt; &kaddressbook;"
msgstr "&kmail; -&gt; &kaddressbook;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Dragging a message from <ulink url=\"help:/kmail2/using-kmail.html#the-mail-"
"reader-window\">&kmail;'s Headers pane</ulink> to the icon for "
"&kaddressbook; (<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"kaddressbook-sidebar-icon.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject></guiicon>) will create a contact from the email address "
"of the sender, unless a contact with that name already exists. A dialog box "
"notifies you of this action."
msgstr ""
"Vlečenje sporočila iz <ulink url=\"help:/kmail2/using-kmail.html#the-mail-"
"reader-window\">podokna z glavami &kmail;</ulink> na ikono za &kaddressbook; "
"(<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"kaddressbook-"
"sidebar-icon.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guiicon>) bo ustvaril stik iz e-pošte naslov pošiljatelja, razen če kontakt "
"s tem imenom že obstaja. O tem dejanju vas obvesti pogovorno okno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kaddressbook; -&gt; &korganizer; To-do List"
msgstr "&kaddressbook; -&gt; &korganizer; Seznam opravil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:413
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Dragging any number of entries from <ulink url=\"help:/kaddressbook/using-"
"kaddressbook.html\">&kaddressbook;'s main window</ulink> to the icon for "
"&korganizer;'s To-do List (<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"todo-list-sidebar-icon.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon>) will create a new To-do with "
"&quot;Meeting&quot; as the title and the selected contacts as attendees."
msgstr ""
"Vlečenje poljubnega števila vnosov iz <ulink url=\"help:/kaddressbook/using-"
"kaddressbook.html\">glavnega okna &kaddressbook;</ulink> na ikono za Seznam "
"opravil &korganizer; (<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"todo-list-sidebar-icon.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject></guiicon>) bo ustvaril novo opravilo z &quot; "
"Srečanje&quot; kot naslov in izbrane kontakte kot udeležence."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:435
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kaddressbook; -&gt; &korganizer; Calendar"
msgstr "&kaddressbook; -&gt; &korganizer; Koledar"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:437
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Dragging any number of entries from <ulink url=\"help:/kaddressbook/using-"
"kaddressbook.html\">&kaddressbook;'s main window</ulink> to the icon for "
"&korganizer;'s Calendar (<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"calendar-sidebar-icon.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon>) will create a new Event with "
"&quot;Meeting&quot; as the title and the selected contacts as attendees."
msgstr ""
"Vlečenje poljubnega števila vnosov iz <ulink url=\"help:/kaddressbook/using-"
"kaddressbook.html\">glavnega okna &kaddressbook;</ulink> na ikono koledarja "
"&korganizer; (<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"calendar-sidebar-icon.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject></guiicon>) bo ustvaril nov dogodek s &quot;Meeting&quot; "
"kot naslov in izbrane kontakte kot udeležence."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:463
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Summary View"
msgstr "Pogled povzetka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default view when starting &kontact; for the first time is the Summary "
"View. It shows an overview of the most relevant information provided by the "
"selected &kontact; components. These can be imminent appointments or "
"birthdays, due to-dos, new messages &etc; Which information is shown is "
"configurable by selecting the corresponding components in the <link linkend="
"\"configuration\"> &kontact; configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Privzeti pogled ob prvem zagonu &kontakt;a je pogled povzetka. Prikazuje "
"pregled najpomembnejših informacij, ki jih zagotavljajo izbrane komponente "
"&kontakt;a. To so lahko bližajoči se sestanki ali rojstni dnevi, opravki, "
"nova sporočila itd. Katere informacije so prikazane, lahko nastavite z "
"izbiro ustreznih komponent v <link linkend=\"configuration\"> pogovornem "
"oknu za konfiguracijo &kontakt;a</link>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kontact;'s Summary View</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogled povzetka &kontact;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:477
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kontact;'s Summary View</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogled povzetka &kontact;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>&kontact;'s Summary View</para>"
msgstr "<para>Pogled povzetka &kontact;</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:495
#, no-c-format
msgid "Repositioning Summary View Components"
msgstr "Prestavljanje komponent pogleda povzetka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Summary View allows you to change where the components are in the view "
"itself. So, if you prefer to have your Special Dates in the lower left and "
"your To-dos in the upper right, you can rearrange the Summary View to "
"reflect that."
msgstr ""
"Pogled povzetka vam omogoča, da spremenite, kje so komponente v samem "
"pogledu. Torej, če želite imeti posebne datume v spodnjem levem kotu in "
"opravila v zgornjem desnem kotu, lahko preuredite pogled povzetka, da bo to "
"odražal."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Repositioning components in the Summary View is as simple as dragging them "
"to the new location you want them to be in. Hold down the &Ctrl; key, click "
"and hold on the gray title area of the component and drag the component to "
"wherever you want it to be. Note that this positioning is done compared to "
"other components. So you can move the Mail component to be below the To-do "
"component in the view, but you cannot place it in a specific position. If "
"you have only one component in your Summary View, the only option is to move "
"it between the two columns of the view; two components can either be two in "
"one column or one in each column; and so on and so forth. Whenever you are "
"dragging a component, you will see a small preview box following your mouse "
"around showing you the component."
msgstr ""
"Sprememba položaja komponent v pogledu povzetka je tako preprosta, kot da "
"jih povlečete na novo mesto, kjer želite, da so. Držite &Ctrl; kliknite in "
"držite sivo naslovno območje komponente ter povlecite komponento kamor koli "
"želite. Upoštevajte, da je to pozicioniranje izvedeno v primerjavi z drugimi "
"komponentami. Torej lahko premaknete komponento pošte pod komponento "
"Opravila v pogledu, ne morete pa je postaviti na določen položaj. Če imate v "
"pogledu povzetka samo eno komponento, je edina možnost, da jo premikate med "
"obema stolpcema pogleda; dve komponenti sta lahko dve v enem stolpcu ali ena "
"v vsakem stolpcu; in tako naprej in tako naprej. Kadar koli povlečete "
"komponento, boste videli majhno polje za predogled, ki sledi vaši miški in "
"vam prikazuje komponento."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:516
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Rearranging &kontact;'s Summary View</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Preurejanje pogleda povzetka &kontact;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:520
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Rearranging &kontact;'s Summary View</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Preurejanje pogleda povzetka &kontact;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Rearranging &kontact;'s Summary View</para>"
msgstr "<para>Preurejanje pogleda povzetka &kontact;</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:535
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring &kontact;"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje &kontact;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:538
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kontact; Configuration Window"
msgstr "&kontact; Konfiguracijsko okno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:540
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When selecting the <guimenuitem>Configure &kontact;</guimenuitem> action "
"from the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu, the &kontact; configuration "
"dialog is shown. It provides a list of the configurations for all the active "
"components of &kontact;. You can click the <guilabel>&gt;</guilabel> symbol "
"next to the component name to expand the tree so that you can view the "
"options for that component. Selecting one of the configuration options under "
"a heading will bring up that configuration section on the right."
msgstr ""
"Ko v meniju <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> izberete dejanje "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kontact;</guimenuitem>, se &kontact; prikazano je "
"konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno. Ponuja seznam konfiguracij za vse aktivne "
"komponente &kontact;. Lahko kliknete simbol <guilabel>&gt;</guilabel> poleg "
"imena komponente, da razširite drevo in si lahko ogledate možnosti za to "
"komponento. Če izberete eno od možnosti konfiguracije pod naslovom, se "
"prikaže ta razdelek konfiguracije na desni."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:551
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kontact;'s Configuration Window</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Konfiguracijsko okno &kontact;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:555
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kontact;'s Configuration Window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Konfiguracijsko okno &kontact;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:558
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>&kontact;'s Configuration Window</para>"
msgstr "<para>Konfiguracijsko okno &kontact;</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:565
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By checking the box next to the component title you select the component to "
"be visible in the Side Pane and the Summary View. The component is loaded "
"and shown in the Main Window when clicking on its icon in the Side Pane. By "
"unchecking the check box the component is removed from the Side Pane and "
"Summary View. Changes become effective by clicking the <guibutton>Apply</"
"guibutton> or <guibutton>OK</guibutton> buttons."
msgstr ""
"Če potrdite polje poleg naslova komponente, izberete komponento, ki bo vidna "
"v stranskem podoknu in v pogledu povzetka. Komponenta se naloži in prikaže v "
"glavnem oknu, ko kliknete njeno ikono v stranskem podoknu. Če počistite "
"potrditveno polje, se komponenta odstrani iz stranskega podokna in pogleda "
"povzetka. Spremembe stopijo v veljavo s klikom na gumb <guibutton>Uporabi</"
"guibutton> ali <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:574
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also configure individual components by clicking on the "
"corresponding icon in the Side Pane and then selecting the menu item "
"<guimenuitem>Configure <replaceable>application name</replaceable></"
"guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Posamezne komponente lahko konfigurirate tudi tako, da kliknete ustrezno "
"ikono v stranskem podoknu in nato izberete menijsko postavko "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj <replaceable>ime aplikacije</replaceable></"
"guimenuitem> v meniju <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> ."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>&kontact; Settings Menu When &kmail; is Selected</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kontact; Meni z nastavitvami Ko &kmail; je izbrano</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:586
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kontact; Settings Menu When &kmail; is Selected</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kontact; Meni z nastavitvami Ko &kmail; je izbrano</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:589
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>&kontact; Settings Menu When &kmail; is Selected</para>"
msgstr "<para>&kontact; Meni z nastavitvami Ko &kmail; je izbran</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:599
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring &kontact;'s Summary View"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje &kontact; pogleda povzetka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you select <guilabel>Summaries</guilabel> in the &kontact; settings "
"dialog, a page is displayed that allows you to select which summary plugins "
"&kontact; should show in its summary view. Here is a brief list of the "
"currently available plugins and what they do:"
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete <guilabel>Povzetki</guilabel> v mapi &kontact; pogovorno okno z "
"nastavitvami, se prikaže stran, na kateri lahko izberete, kateri povzetek "
"vtičnikov &kontact; mora biti prikazan v pogledu povzetka. Tukaj je kratek "
"seznam trenutno razpoložljivih vtičnikov in njihovega delovanja:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:608
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Summary Selection</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Izbira povzetka</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:614
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Summary Selection</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izbira povzetka</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:616
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Summary Selection</para>"
msgstr "<para>Izbira povzetka</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:621
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kontact; Summary Plugins: Calendar"
msgstr "&kontact; Povzetek vtičnikov: Koledar"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:623
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>Calendar</quote> plugin for &kontact;'s Summary View adds an area "
"in the view labeled <guilabel>Upcoming Events</guilabel>. This will display "
"any events that currently apply."
msgstr ""
"Vtičnik <quote>Koledar</quote> za pogled povzetka &kontact; doda območje v "
"pogled z oznako <guilabel>Prihajajoči dogodki</guilabel>. To bo prikazalo "
"vse dogodke, ki trenutno veljajo."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:630
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kontact; Calendar Summary Plugin</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kontact; Vtičnik za povzetek koledarja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:636
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kontact; Calendar Summary Plugin</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kontact; Vtičnik za povzetek koledarja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:639
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>&kontact; Calendar Summary Plugin</para>"
msgstr "<para>&kontact; Vtičnik za povzetek koledarja</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:648
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kontact; Summary Plugins: Mail"
msgstr "&kontact; Povzetek vtičnikov: Pošta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:650
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>Mail</quote> plugin for &kontact;'s Summary View adds an area in "
"the view labeled <guilabel>New Messages</guilabel>. This area is updated "
"every time you receive new messages to inform you how many of these messages "
"there are and which folder they are in."
msgstr ""
"Vtičnik <quote>Pošta</quote> za pogled povzetka &kontact; doda območje v "
"pogledu z oznako <guilabel>Nova sporočila</guilabel>. To področje se "
"posodobi vsakič, ko prejmete nova sporočila, da vas obvesti, koliko teh "
"sporočil je na voljo in v kateri mapi so."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:658
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kontact; Mail Summary Plugin</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kontact; vtičnik poštnega povzetka</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:664
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kontact; Mail Summary Plugin</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kontact; Vtičnik poštnega povzetka</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:667
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>&kontact; Mail Summary Plugin</para>"
msgstr "<para>&kontact; Vtičnik poštnega povzetka</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:677
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kontact; Summary Plugins: To-do List"
msgstr "&kontact; Povzetek vtičnikov: Seznam opravil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:679
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>To-do List</quote> plugin for &kontact;'s Summary View adds an "
"area in the view labeled <guilabel>Pending To-dos</guilabel>. This area "
"contains all current to-dos, including ones that have been completed. It "
"displays the title of the to-do, the percentage of completion, and the "
"current status of the to-do. Note that you can purge all completed to-dos "
"via the &kontact; To-do List. Clicking on a to-do's title will currently do "
"nothing."
msgstr ""
"Vtičnik <quote>Seznam opravil</quote> za pogled povzetka &kontact; doda "
"območje v pogledu z oznako <guilabel>Čakajoča opravila</guilabel>. To "
"področje vsebuje vsa trenutna opravila, vključno s tistimi, ki so bila "
"dokončana. Prikaže naslov opravila, odstotek dokončanja in trenutno stanje "
"opravila. Upoštevajte, da lahko izbrišete vsa dokončana opravila preko "
"&kontact; Seznam opravil. S klikom na naslov opravila trenutno ne boste "
"naredili ničesar."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:690
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kontact; To-do List Summary Plugin</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kontact; Vtičnik povzeteka Seznama opravil</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:696
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kontact; To-do List Summary Plugin</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kontact; Vtičnik povzeteka seznama opravil</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:699
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>&kontact; To-do List Summary Plugin</para>"
msgstr "<para>&kontact; Vtičnik povzeteka seznama opravil</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:708
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kontact; Summary Plugins: Special Dates"
msgstr "&kontact; Povzetek vtičnikov: posebni datumi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:710
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>Special Dates</quote> plugin for &kontact;'s Summary View adds an "
"area in the view labeled <guilabel>Upcoming Special Dates</guilabel>. This "
"area contains information based on the criteria selected in the "
"configuration area of the plugin in &kontact;'s Summary View configuration. "
"The <quote>Special Dates</quote> plugin is especially useful because it can "
"display birthdays, anniversaries, holidays, and special occasions from both "
"the calendar and the contact list in one place."
msgstr ""
"Vtičnik <quote>Posebni datumi</quote> za pogled povzetka &kontact; doda "
"območje v pogledu z oznako <guilabel>Prihajajoči posebni datumi</guilabel>. "
"To področje vsebuje informacije, ki temeljijo na merilih, izbranih v "
"konfiguracijskem območju vtičnika v konfiguraciji pogleda povzetka "
"&kontact;. Vtičnik <quote>Posebni datumi</quote> je še posebej uporaben, ker "
"lahko na enem mestu prikaže rojstne dneve, obletnice, praznike in posebne "
"priložnosti iz koledarja in seznama stikov."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:721
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kontact; Special Dates Plugin</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kontact; Vtičnik za posebne datume</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:727
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kontact; Special Dates Plugin</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kontact; Vtičnik za posebne datume</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:730
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>&kontact; Special Dates Plugin</para>"
msgstr "<para>&kontact; Vtičnik za posebne datume</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:743
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kontact; On the Command Line"
msgstr "&kontact; V ukazni vrstici"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:745
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kontact; has several command line arguments that can be used for certain "
"actions."
msgstr ""
"&kontact; ima več argumentov ukazne vrstice, ki jih je mogoče uporabiti za "
"določena dejanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:748
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First of all, &kontact; supports command line arguments that all &kde-"
"frameworks;/&Qt; applications support, see the man pages qt6options and "
"kf6options."
msgstr ""
"Najprej &kontact; podpira argumente ukazne vrstice, da vsi &kde-frameworks;/"
"&Qt; podpora za aplikacije, glejte man strani qt6options in kf6options."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:752
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kontact; also supports several command line arguments specific to it."
msgstr ""
"&kontact; podpira tudi več argumentov ukazne vrstice, specifičnih zanj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:756
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Line Arguments"
msgstr "Argumenti ukazne vrstice"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:759
#, no-c-format
msgid "Module-related Arguments"
msgstr "Argumenti, povezani z modulom"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:761
#, no-c-format
msgid "To get a list of available &kontact; modules, you can type:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite pridobiti seznam razpoložljivih &kontact; modulov, lahko vnesete:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:763
#, no-c-format
msgid "<prompt>&percnt;</prompt> <command>kontact --list</command>"
msgstr "<prompt>&percnt;</prompt> <command>kontact --list</command>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:767
#, no-c-format
msgid "Then, to start &kontact; with a module active, type:"
msgstr "Nato za zagon &kontact; z aktivnim modulom vnesite:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:769
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>&percnt;</prompt> <command>kontact --module <replaceable>moduleName</"
"replaceable></command>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>&percnt;</prompt> <command>kontact --module <replaceable>imeModula</"
"replaceable></command>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:773
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Where <replaceable>moduleName</replaceable> is one of the modules obtained "
"using the previous command."
msgstr ""
"Pri čemer je <replaceable>imeModula</replaceable> eden od modulov, "
"pridobljen s prejšnjim ukazom."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:779
#, no-c-format
msgid "Startup-related Arguments"
msgstr "Argumenti, povezani z zagonom"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:781
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To start &kontact; in iconified mode<footnote><para>Iconified mode is also "
"called minimized; it is when the application window is hidden and the "
"application is available only in the taskbar.</para></footnote>, you can "
"type:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite zagnati &kontact; v ikoniziranem načinu<footnote><para>Ikonizirani "
"način se imenuje tudi minimiziran; je, ko je okno aplikacije skrito in je "
"aplikacija na voljo samo v opravilni vrstici.</para></footnote>, lahko "
"vnesete:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:786
#, no-c-format
msgid "<prompt>&percnt;</prompt> <command>kontact --iconify</command>"
msgstr "<prompt>&percnt;</prompt> <command>kontact --iconify</command>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:798
#, no-c-format
msgid "Under The Hood"
msgstr "Pod pokrovom"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:800
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kontact; makes extensive use of several &kde; key technologies, most "
"notably KParts and &DBus;."
msgstr ""
"&kontact; obsežno uporablja več &kde; ključnih tehnologij, predvsem KParts "
"in &DBus;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:803
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &GUI; integration of the components is done by plugins providing KParts "
"versions of the applications. This only needs a thin additional layer on top "
"of the already existing code of the stand-alone applications."
msgstr ""
"&GUI; integracijo komponent izvajajo vtičniki, ki zagotavljajo različice "
"aplikacij Kparts. Za to je potreben samo tanek dodaten sloj na vrhu že "
"obstoječe kode samostojnih aplikacij."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:808
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For communication between the components &DBus; is used. This has the nice "
"characteristic that it is completely transparent to whether the application "
"is run stand-alone or embedded as KPart into &kontact;. When running inside "
"of &kontact; an efficient in-process mode of &DBus; is used."
msgstr ""
"Za komunikacijo med komponentami &DBus; se uporablja. To ima lepo lastnost, "
"da je popolnoma pregledno, ali se aplikacija izvaja samostojno ali je "
"vdelana kot KPart v &kontact;. Pri izvajanju znotraj &kontact; učinkovit "
"medprocesni način &DBus; se uporablja."

